'''DZAD-TV''' is a commercial television owned by [[ABS-CBN Broadcasting Corporation]]. It's studio & transmitter is located at Ground floor, Philamlife Building, Kumitang Ibaba, Hilltop, [[Batangas City]]. The station can also be seen in some parts of [[Metro Manila]].
==ABS-CBN TV-10 Local Programs== *[[Gising Na Maagang Southern Tagalog]] (simulcast over ABS-CBN TV-24 Lucena,TV-40 Antipolo, TV-46 San Pablo and TV-38 Lipa) *[[TV Patrol Southern Tagalog]] (simulcast over ABS-CBN TV-24 Lucena,TV-40 Rizal, TV-46 San Pablo, TV-11 Occ. Mindoro, TV-38 Lipa and TV-32 Tagaytay) *[[Mag TV Na|MAG TV Na, Atin 'To!]] (simulcast over ABS-CBN TV-24 Lucena, TV-40 Antipolo, TV-46 San Pablo, TV-11 Occ. Mindoro and TV-38 Lipa and ABS-CBN Stations in Northern, Central Luzon)
